<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.9">
<l>nīraḻal vāṉāy neṭunilaṅ kālāy niṉṟaniṉ nīrmaiyai niṉaintō</l>
<l>cīrkkeḻu kōtai yeṉṉala tilaḷeṉ ṟaṉṉatōr tēṟṟaṉmai tāṉō</l>
<l>pārkkeḻu pavvat tāramu taṉaiya pāvaiyaip pāvamcey tēṉuk</l>
<l>kāraḻa lōmpu mantaṇaṉ tōṭṭa mākaniṉ maṉattuvait tāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Was it considering your nature which is eternal as water, fire, as the heavens,</l>
<l rend="indent">the vast earth, and as the wind,</l>
<l>Or was it thinking, “except for me,” she of the fine, full hair garland</l>
<l rend="indent">is without any support?</l>
<l>This girl, who is like the rare nectar of the bright oceans of the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">for me who has committed sins,</l>
<l>You placed in your mind like a garden of a priest</l>
<l rend="indent">who maintains the rare fires.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
